imdb.plot outline: MTV scours the viral video landscape and curates only the funniest, most compelling music themed videos. In each episode, only the best of the best are presented by our fun MTV tone of "voice", irreverent sense of humor, and wrapped together with innovative graphics inspired by the mobile video space, producing a video-clip watching experience we can all relate to.
